{"tid":1261761,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"达哥vs館長","createTime":"2019-06-27T11:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T17:27:15.000Z","uid":3083,"like":236,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5b97a77652f0011007cd2b8fe15d4aef2f42bacb","tid":1261761,"uid":3083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aYi1SQi6zjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaYi1SQi6zjk&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=6b1a08a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aYi1SQi6zjk</a><br />\n<br />\n近排館長因為搞左個反共遊行，又係直播時反共，所以比直播平台同埋好多廠商封殺，損失每月數百萬台幣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但係</strong>，佢并冇選擇沉默，佢無向錢低頭，佢利用佢嘅影響力去同台灣人講，千萬不要受中媒洗腦影響去赤化台灣。佢亦表明如共狗夠膽攻過來，佢第一個上前頂。<br />\n<br />\n相反达哥，錢同骨氣，佢選擇左錢。唔該盲粉你地醒下，依啲咁嘅人真係仲值得你去支持？<br />\n<br />\n我已經unsubscribe 哂佢所有野，希望你仲有廉恥以後唔好再開台"},{"pid":"c87ae6581e594eaee084081bb46ea0dfa59b4518","tid":1261761,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":64,"score":-61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"迖要供樓 要養團隊 <br />\n館長自己大把野撈"},{"pid":"28afdc2c8506e1258744e4075f2cbff2f057bec9","tid":1261761,"uid":191815,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"咪再借其他人幫達哥刷名氣啦<br />\n真心達哥𠵱家仲係WFC"},{"pid":"7886e427bd97d0536089cfa57a903cd26d6f2abc","tid":1261761,"uid":25367,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"并你老母，你自己都係支那人"},{"pid":"b6da1b060a0a28e7ee70e7044613dec43c282513","tid":1261761,"uid":77769,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"台灣同香港既生活指數。。。"},{"pid":"53db4f191f828a1ddabd7a0aba6ab3a2329ebf56","tid":1261761,"uid":31200,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"即刻subscribe館長支持下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc886837aa17f753ec56540bc3b980878ca5d51","